questions.subject: ComfyUI_Custom_Nodes_AlekPet
questions.question: What is the purpose of the node's changelog section?
questions.answer: The changelog section lists updates and contributions to the node.

questions.subject: ComfyUI_Custom_Nodes_AlekPet
questions.question: Why can't the ComfyUI server overwrite files?
questions.answer: The server does not support overwriting files as a security measure. New images are created in the temporary folder, which is cleared when ComfyUI is restarted.

questions.subject: ComfyUI_Custom_Nodes_AlekPet
questions.question: How does the node handle image use?
questions.answer: The node uses the PoseNode and TranslateCLIPTextEncodeNode to process images and translate Russian text to English.

questions.subject: ComfyUI_Custom_Nodes_AlekPet/PoseNode
